  "detailed_description": "<strong>The Factory Must Grow</strong> is a 3D first-person factory builder where you mine resources, craft machines, and research technology. Begin by unlocking your first technology, then expand into a sprawling, multi-layered production empire. From small setups to massive systems, your imagination is the only limit!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Dynamic Terrain Generation:</strong> Create unique maps every time, offering endless ways to challenge and customize your gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169270/extras/a4dc4dd249695acb9cad5fba22cea29c.poster.avif?t=1726470139\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169270/extras/a4dc4dd249695acb9cad5fba22cea29c.webm?t=1726470139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169270/extras/a4dc4dd249695acb9cad5fba22cea29c.mp4?t=1726470139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Diverse Technology Tree:</strong> Unlock and research 22 technologies—tailor your strategy to build the ultimate factory your way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169270/extras/6104a0aecb863a25b40741b6e6f52a3c.poster.avif?t=1726470139\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169270/extras/6104a0aecb863a25b40741b6e6f52a3c.webm?t=1726470139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169270/extras/6104a0aecb863a25b40741b6e6f52a3c.mp4?t=1726470139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Wide Range of Machines:</strong> Automate your production with 10 distinct machine types, each adding depth to your assembly lines.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169270/extras/9ece85500d15a82f75f0c86a15820dbf.poster.avif?t=1726470139\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169270/extras/9ece85500d15a82f75f0c86a15820dbf.webm?t=1726470139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169270/extras/9ece85500d15a82f75f0c86a15820dbf.mp4?t=1726470139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>The Factory Must Grow</strong> is a 3D first-person factory builder where you mine resources, craft machines, and research technology. Begin by unlocking your first technology, then expand into a sprawling, multi-layered production empire. From small setups to massive systems, your imagination is the only limit!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Dynamic Terrain Generation:</strong> Create unique maps every time, offering endless ways to challenge and customize your gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169270/extras/a4dc4dd249695acb9cad5fba22cea29c.poster.avif?t=1726470139\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169270/extras/a4dc4dd249695acb9cad5fba22cea29c.webm?t=1726470139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169270/extras/a4dc4dd249695acb9cad5fba22cea29c.mp4?t=1726470139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Diverse Technology Tree:</strong> Unlock and research 22 technologies—tailor your strategy to build the ultimate factory your way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169270/extras/6104a0aecb863a25b40741b6e6f52a3c.poster.avif?t=1726470139\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169270/extras/6104a0aecb863a25b40741b6e6f52a3c.webm?t=1726470139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169270/extras/6104a0aecb863a25b40741b6e6f52a3c.mp4?t=1726470139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Wide Range of Machines:</s